724432f-b.text:
West End Avenue, west side, at W.63rd Street. The views are southwestward across the New York Central Railroad yards toward the Hudson River and the
grain elevator of the railroad company.
View 2 shows the new West Side Express Vehicular Highway.
P.L.Sperr  Viewl: March 19, 1930
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: December 19, 1937
